## @api.onchange：动态更新UI

```python
@api.onchange('demo')
def onchange_demo(self):
    # 循环多条记录
    for rec in self:
        # 判断字段是否存在
        if rec.demo:
            if rec.demo < 0:
                # 弱提醒
                return {'warning': {'title': "title", 'message': "message"}}
```

## Odoo Controllers Website

> Controllers/*.python
> 访问 `odoo网址/test`

```python
# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-
from odoo import http
import json


class HttpTest(http.Controller):

    @http.route('/test/', type='http', auth='public', website=True)
    def index(self, **kw):
        test = kw
        return json.dumps({'test': test})
